Class AccessibleDisplayScreenReaderImplementation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hatemile.implementation.AccessibleDisplayScreenReaderImplementation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessibleDisplay

    public class AccessibleDisplayScreenReaderImplementation
extends Object
implements AccessibleDisplay
    The AccessibleDisplayScreenReaderImplementation class is official implementation of AccessibleDisplay for screen readers.
